Manufacturing practices
Sustainability features
This product has sustainability features recognized by trusted certifications.
Manufacturing practices
The leather in this product was produced by a Leather Working Group (LWG) certified tannery, supporting more-responsible leather production. LWG brand members may make on-product claims if they have submitted a sourcing declaration and 100% of the leather is produced by a LWG certified tannery.
As certified by
Leather Working Group
Learn more about Leather Working Group

Leather Working Group

Leather Working Group certifies tanneries with more sustainable manufacturing practices focused on resource efficiency, reduced waste generation and emissions, better chemical management and increased traceability. LWG brand members may make claims on meeting a number of criteria, including submitting a sourcing declaration stating the percentage of leather purchased from LWG-certified facilities. A claim can only be made when a product contains leather as the prominent material and 100% of the leather was produced by a LWG-certified tannery.
